OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter man found dead
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder after another man was found
OL,8,Fdead at a property.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FHigginshaw Lane, in Royton, Oldham,
OL,12,Fshortly after 10am on Sunday, 8 March,
OL,13,Ffollowing reports of a "concern for
OL,14,Fthe welfare".
OL,16,FA 48-year-old died at the scene,
OL,17,Fpolice said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
