PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773076277
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter man found dead
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) has
OL,7,Fconfirmed that a 49-year-old man has
OL,8,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,9,Fand he remains in police custody for
OL,10,Fquestioning.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Rachel Smith, from
OL,13,Fthe force's Major Incident Team,
OL,14,Fsought to reassure the public that
OL,15,Fthere is no wider threat to the local
OL,16,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773076277
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter man found dead
OL,6,FShe said: "Our thoughts remain with
OL,7,Fthe victim's loved ones. We understand
OL,8,Fthe concern this incident may cause
OL,9,Facross the local community, but I
OL,10,Fwould like to reassure you that we
OL,11,Fbelieve this to be an isolated
OL,12,Fincident."
OL,14,FShe added that while the investigation
OL,15,Fis in its early stages, police are
OL,16,Fkeeping an "open mind" regarding the
OL,17,Fcircumstances.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773076277
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter man found dead
OL,6,F"We are open to all lines of
OL,7,Fenquiry...and we are conducting
OL,8,Fextensive enquiries to establish the
OL,9,Ffull circumstances of this incident,"
OL,10,Fshe said.
OL,12,FResidents have been told to expect a
OL,13,Fcontinued and increased police
OL,14,Fpresence throughout the next few days
OL,15,Fas forensic teams and officers conduct
OL,16,Fdoor-to-door enquiries.
OL,18,FPolice are appealing for anyone with
OL,19,Finformation to call 101 quoting log
OL,20,Fnumber 972 of 08/03/26 or contact
OL,21,FCrimestoppers on 0800 555 111.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
